CatDescriptText: The rest of the sign behind the group of people reads, "For Lieutenant Governor - Roy E. Furman, For Secretary Internal Affairs - Genevieve Blatt, For Judge of Superior Court - Chester H. Rhodes, F. Clair Ross, Rob[?]ert E. Woodside, Jr.,  Representative in Congress, 28th District - [?]man Eberharter, Representative in the General Assembly 1st . . . - Daniel E. Veronica[?], . . .Anderson."
TitMainTitle: Woman and six men standing in front of voting place, with sign in background reading, "We Need a Leader in Harrisburg, Vote Democratic, for Governor George M. Leader"
